# MySQL Docker stack
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Database files / volumes if bind-mounted locally
MySQL-docker/data/
MySQL-docker/mysql_data/
# Real secret values — commit *.example templates instead, not the live files
MySQL-docker/secrets/*.txt
!MySQL-docker/secrets/*.example
